cs.SY, cs.DC, cs.LG, cs.NA, cs.CE 

This paper deals with optimization of power grids, which involves a combination of control systems (cs.SY), distributed computing (cs.DC), and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The paper also discusses the use of graph partitioning algorithms (cs.NA) and their impact on the performance of the optimization algorithm. Finally, the paper is relevant to the field of civil engineering (cs.CE) as it deals with the optimization of power grids.
